value.string: Oceanfront 21.73 acre parcel below Camp Maluhia. Spectacular views overlooking the Kahakuloa coastline and Makamakaole Gulch. Conveniently located with direct access to Kahekili Highway, a paved state highway. Underground utilities, private water system. A septic system must be installed for building permit approval. Showings by appointment only. Contact a local Realtor for more information or to setup an appointment. Please do not disturb neighbors. SUBMIT OFFER!!!!

WTIO 1162P- Great opportunity to own a studio unit at the Whaler on Kaanapali Beach. This unit boasts ocean and mountain views and overlooks the beautifully manicured courtyard. Interval "P" is 2 weeks of ownership every year from July 22 to August 5. The Whaler is situated along the world-renowned Kaanapali Beach. The Whaler offers amenities such as a beach side pool, BBQs, spa, sauna, workout gym, salon, underground parking and a business hub center. The courtyard boasts a Koi fish pond and plenty of green space to enjoy this tranquil venue featuring the best of Maui. Boutique shops and award-winning restaurants are nearby. The Buyer will have occupancy starting July 22, 2016.
